                                     (310) 235-6884
                                     (503) 326-2081
                                     (619) 557-6538
                                     (415) 975-4350
                                     (206) 553-0645
        * Library
          Telephone: The Economic Analysis & Information staff is available
          for phone assistance from 9:00 AM to 1130 AM and 1:30 PM to 4:00 PM
          at (415) 975-4350.
          Location: The office is open from 8:00 AM to 4:00 PM and is located
          at:


   Bureau of Labor Statistics
   71 Stevenson Street
   Suite 600,
   San Francisco, CA 94105
